Section: Tweaks
Homepage: https://github.com/ibrahim2100/instv3
Description: Download anything, hide the noise, browse invisibly — in Arabic or English.
 .
 Albrhi puts a download button where Instagram should have put one, strips the feed
 back to the people you actually follow, and stops the app reporting what you watch.
 Everything lives in a settings panel that looks like it shipped with the app.
 .
 ▍DOWNLOADS
 A native download button sits in the action row of every post and reel, beside the
 save icon. One tap grabs the highest quality available and writes it straight to
 Photos — optionally into its own album.
 .
 Stories and view-once DMs get their own button. Reels can be saved as video or as
 the original audio track. Profile pictures download in full HD on a long press.
 .
 ▍DOWNLOAD CENTER
 A real queue behind it all: pause, resume, retry and cancel, several transfers at
 once, and downloads that keep running after you leave the app. Duplicate links are
 detected, finished files are cleared once they reach Photos, and a searchable
 history records everything you have saved.
 .
 ▍A QUIETER FEED
 Remove ads, sponsored posts, suggested posts, suggested accounts, suggested reels,
 Threads posts, Meta AI, the friends map, trending searches and the explore grid.
 Hide the stories tray — or the entire feed.
 .
 ▍PRIVACY
 Watch stories without sending a seen receipt, and decide per story when to send one.
 View-once photos and videos stay unseen until you tap the eye button on that exact
 message. Hide the typing indicator and disable screenshot detection.
 .
 ▍REELS
 Tap to pause or mute instead of liking. Keep the progress scrubber visible. Stop
 reels unmuting themselves. Hide the header and the blend button.
 .
 ▍CONFIRMATIONS
 An optional prompt before liking, following, reposting, calling, commenting or
 sending a voice message — so a mis-tap never turns into a notification.
 .
 ▍BUILT TO FIT IN
 Full Arabic and English with automatic right-to-left layout. SF Symbols, a
 customisable accent colour, dark mode, and a settings panel opened by holding the
 menu button on your profile. Includes a diagnostics page that reports what the
 tweak actually sees on your build and files a bug report in one tap.
 .
 ▍TESTED ON
 Instagram 410.1.0. Not chosen for any principled reason — that is simply the newest
 build the developer's phone will still accept. The phone has served with honour and
 is now retired to a life of testing tweaks.
 .
 Newer Instagram versions will most likely work: nothing here depends on a version
 number, and the tweak looks up what it needs at runtime. But "most likely" is doing
 real work in that sentence, and honesty costs nothing.
 .
 ▍BETA
 This is a pre-release. Features are tested but your Instagram build may differ from
 ours — if something misbehaves, Settings › Diagnostics writes the report for you,
 Instagram version included, so we stop guessing and start fixing.
 .
 Developed by Ibrahim Ismail AL-Rahn. An educational and corrective derivative of
 SCInsta by SoCuul, rebuilt with AI assistance to improve code quality, design,
 performance and user experience. Free and open source under the GNU GPL v3, with
 original authorship fully credited and preserved.
